## Generation pattern

- Tool: OpenAI DALL-E 3 (`/v1/images/generations`), `model:"dall-e-3"`, `size:"1024x1792"`, `quality:"standard"`.
- Downsized in Pillow (LANCZOS) from 1024×1792 → 1024×1280 to match spec aspect.
- Script: `scripts/gen_biome_images.py` (UNCOMMITTED — contains inline OpenAI key for reproducibility; do not commit. To regen, read the key from `~/Desktop/Hive/api.rtf` per `reference_api_keys.md`).
- Generation log: `/tmp/wg_biome_gen.jsonl`.
- All 6 generated first-attempt — no retries spent.

